{"tid":35020,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【靈異/偵探】頭先屋企隻貓發生不可思議事件 大家幫幫手唸","createTime":"2016-12-11T20:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T06:21:18.000Z","uid":1895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b016a5269d4da7af70c086852880e807c24bf77e","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:39:07.000Z","msg":"成件事係咁,頭先屋企隻貓離奇失蹤左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說我頭先十一點幾就同女朋友傾電話打機 一直傾到兩點幾<br />\n咁女朋友就話想見下隻貓 咁我就打算搵佢出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來我以為佢會係平時最鐘意哩埋個個窿個到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知無!跟住我就反轉成間房搵佢啦 都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就開始驚啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通我放左佢出廳玩?咁我就call埋我個妹 兩個人夜媽媽兩點幾係屋企搵貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知搵曬佢平時最鐘意哩埋既地方都搵唔到 直頭反轉曬成間屋都見唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就去問屋企人有無見過 佢話佢夜晚十二點幾返到屋企個陣見到佢係我房門口 話我放左佢出廳 但唔知我有無比佢入返房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我同個妹就開始驚啦 屌 間屋唔係大 可以去得邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我檢查過曬屋企d窗同貓窗 完全無問題 無可能有任何跳樓既機會<br />\n跟住我地搵到灰曬 屋企人最後見到佢係凌晨十二點幾<br />\n我自己就唔記得最後幾時見過佢 因為我打緊機都無理到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我同個妹出埋門口走廊搵佢 成層樓兜左一個圈都無發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我媽就落左後樓梯搵 都無發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果我媽第二次出門口搵個陣 就意外發現佢係人地門口個角落頭到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">企</span></span>左係到,係呀 無睇錯呀 我呀媽話見到佢個陣佢係企左係到 跟住就捉左返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實成件事最靈異唔係點搵到佢 同佢企係到<br />\n最不解係隻貓點樣出到屋企門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跪求高登仔幫手唸唸 覺得好靈異<br />\n我老母口供:我十二點返到黎肯定關左鐵閘同木門,同埋見到佢係我門口(貓穿唔過鐵閘)<br />\n我妹口供:我出門口去搵佢個陣 應該無乜可能個陣跟埋我出去<br />\n利申:住紅磡(認真)<br />\n附上 屋企平面圖 同成層樓既平面圖<br />\n麻煩大家幫手唸唸 而家越唸越驚 究竟點出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/l46813buildinga72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fl46813buildinga72.jpg&h=e8800bc4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n39733homed72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn39733homed72.jpg&h=fe8cf465&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dfd7a2c477d6a64b4b1d74b725d0f377f1c94ee","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:40:45.000Z","msg":"第一張圖個d劣質畫既係人地屋企<br />\n第二張圖劣質畫個d係屋企d窗<br />\n紅色點係隻貓企係個到個個位<br />\n好似話係企係到 雙手扶住個墻"},{"pid":"b1471cc2d0e886c858668005d26ea02c02961954","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/044138_1d69a30312a0e98e4c4638a3be0cb1e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F044138_1d69a30312a0e98e4c4638a3be0cb1e7.jpg&h=405c2284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附上貓圖"},{"pid":"b7649d019636fd1c76befffda9dc819d28cbdffa","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dui652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dui652.jpg&h=043c97df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/044235_d80b426498d6b4dbd2ef9d34719e8bf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F044235_d80b426498d6b4dbd2ef9d34719e8bf7.jpg&h=1e8095cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8961dc8c87f6e15a49751a38fc25e151cc63d5a5","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:44:35.000Z","msg":"越唸越驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b3bb11c4a97a13bcbf184e3a3470b1e0adc7f0","tid":35020,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:47:36.000Z","msg":"見你要自推咁慘,回下你喇"},{"pid":"fd05cd16965aa56217cea09e33de0a841bb85076","tid":35020,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:49:08.000Z","msg":"我個隻都走過出去<br />\n<br />\n仲叫到好似bb仔咁<br />\n<br />\n搞到我唔為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後過左一陣先抱返佢入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acd7c431716e13b0af72c037cf19e5e5ce0bf8f","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見你要自推咁慘,回下你喇</blockquote><br />\n凌晨五點 差唔多啦"},{"pid":"ede659ed7a472988611dffd1f4b5a71629856788","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個隻都走過出去<br />\n<br />\n仲叫到好似bb仔咁<br />\n<br />\n搞到我唔為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後過左一陣先抱返佢入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身想唸下佢點出去 跟住防止下次再犯同樣既錯<br />\n點知唸唸下發覺無可能出到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a35790882035ca3a0d538cd4f0eb487383be80d","tid":35020,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:53:36.000Z","msg":"我果隻開大個門都唔會行出去半步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇可能本身匿係屋企某個位，你地開門出去果下佢攝手攝腳跟左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca28aff3bf1f5c7c97d4789487648eb46760b093","tid":35020,"uid":1475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:55:42.000Z","msg":"你間房喺個天井到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37b3a661f846fb1f587e1727db147c773f6e1d9","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你間房喺個天井到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以咁講既 我房個窗望出去係天井黎"},{"pid":"2c33c5230a6ececa173d4536f85b1c46752ec4a0","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果隻開大個門都唔會行出去半步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇可能本身匿係屋企某個位，你地開門出去果下佢攝手攝腳跟左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有唸過 不過我同個妹係反轉成間屋搵唔到先出去搵<br />\n同埋用過佢最鐘意既零食引佢出黎都無反應<br />\n平時係fing幾下個零食包裝袋佢就會狗衝過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb28f74ed9b12a2c00c198624d9cd6d4d7dc405","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/050004_23a270d4a46f422cd3f9a99d80aae5f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F050004_23a270d4a46f422cd3f9a99d80aae5f3.jpg&h=678086fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家佢訓撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9394a7e270ac716cf6cd03b546ac1ee68e88dff5","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:05:33.000Z","msg":"訓先 聽日先推 凌晨無人"},{"pid":"7ed19e227b04daebdd9c9eb8abbdf0a66d285870","tid":35020,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果隻開大個門都唔會行出去半步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇可能本身匿係屋企某個位，你地開門出去果下佢攝手攝腳跟左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有唸過 不過我同個妹係反轉成間屋搵唔到先出去搵<br />\n同埋用過佢最鐘意既零食引佢出黎都無反應<br />\n平時係fing幾下個零食包裝袋佢就會狗衝過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時見到壁虎/甲由佢地會進入狩獵mode咩都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我呀媽份人懵下懵下 有次佢開衣櫃門放衫，隻蠢貓跳左入去佢唔知，閂番門隻貓困左係入面成晚 後尾佢係咁喵聽到聲又搵唔到佢 冇諗過會係衣櫃入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe9fef8f855cc9bfb386246cb4537c79958594c","tid":35020,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:09:27.000Z","msg":"好彩搵得返<br />\n<br />\n貓仔咁得意比人見到實會抱走"},{"pid":"299650a897574fa2f7ba3015dbbac487fac757b3","tid":35020,"uid":1292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:19:38.000Z","msg":"笑左"},{"pid":"26c165c9cb3977501c0d6f4773034be444e4a4aa","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果隻開大個門都唔會行出去半步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇可能本身匿係屋企某個位，你地開門出去果下佢攝手攝腳跟左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有唸過 不過我同個妹係反轉成間屋搵唔到先出去搵<br />\n同埋用過佢最鐘意既零食引佢出黎都無反應<br />\n平時係fing幾下個零食包裝袋佢就會狗衝過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時見到壁虎/甲由佢地會進入狩獵mode咩都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我呀媽份人懵下懵下 有次佢開衣櫃門放衫，隻蠢貓跳左入去佢唔知，閂番門隻貓困左係入面成晚 後尾佢係咁喵聽到聲又搵唔到佢 冇諗過會係衣櫃入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次係關曬成屋既電器 靜曬都聽唔到佢叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e337ca197d8d821885a24fe0f0ebd1bb6d46ded4","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩搵得返<br />\n<br />\n貓仔咁得意比人見到實會抱走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好彩咋 先得四個月大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0b73f8a33d138e6649617017e14c72534357f9","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ef91bfa8bd47922f5079f2ceb433423e7a5c29","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55042dce7fe873596c313eb7c6404903cc3c017e","tid":35020,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"點解咁肯定穿唔過鐵閘？"},{"pid":"26d7cc9f05cff401feefd1a051bc7762929691c9","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解咁肯定穿唔過鐵閘？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鐵閘條&ldquo;啦&rdquo;位係佢個頭既一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bee0c1028ddd6b66ac0364689e2d8491d6ccb2","tid":35020,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}